text.div:
This code system https://example.org/fhir/CodeSystem/BirdPatientBreed defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
canary CanaryA small songbird in the finch family originating from the Macaronesian islands.
cockatiel CockatielA small parrot native to Australia.
parrot ParrotA bird with a curved beak and a strong, zygodactylous feet.
sparrow SparrowA family of small passerine birds.
dove DoveA bird of the pigeon family.
other OtherAny other breed not included in the list.
